gomodel:SYNGO_4797  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Automated change 2024-03-14: GO:0099061 replaced by GO:0098839" , "Rationale: Figure 1B: superresolution microscopy (3D-STORM) showed that Vangl2 colocalized with postsynaptic marker PSD-95 but not with the presynaptic marker Bassoon.\n\nBased on the known transmembrane topology of this protein, \"integral component of ... membrane\" term was selected. As also depicted by authors in Figure 1C.. Experimental description: M&M: \"Hippocampi were dissected from E18.5 mice, and hippocampal neuron culture was performed as previously described\"\n\nantibody:\nmouse anti-Vangl2 (Santa Cruz Biotechnology)" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
